d_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6Y2","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33240,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/19\/hasan-ahl-al-sunnah-gentle\/","url_meta":{"origin":26786,"position":0},"title":"Hasan on Sunnah: O people of Sunnah, be gentle with each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mubarak reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cO followers of the Sunnah! Be gentle with each other, may Allah have mercy on you, for you are surely in the minority of people.\u201d Source: Sharh\u0323 Us\u0323u\u0304l I\u02bbtiqa\u0304d Ahl al-Sunnah 15 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e\u0643\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0635\u0631\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25716,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/09\/umayr-sahabah-easy-living\/","url_meta":{"origin":26786,"position":1},"title":"Umayr on Sahaba: I have not seen anyone easier than the Companions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn \u2018Awn reported: 'Umayr ibn Ishaq, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI have met more companions of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, than anyone before me. I have not seen anyone more lenient in living, nor less harsh than them.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39808,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/19\/accepting-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":26786,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Umar on Qadr: Accepting Allah\u2019s decree at death of a beloved","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Nafi\u2019 reported: A son of Abdullah ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, complained of an illness and Ibn Umar was very distraught over him so much that some people said: We are afraid for this old man because of what might happen to his boy! The boy died\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36091,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/11\/hasan-taqabbal-allahu-minna\/","url_meta":{"origin":26786,"position":3},"title":"Hasan on Eid: May Allah accept from us and from you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hawshab ibn \u2018Aqil reported: I met Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, on the day of Eid and I said, \u201cMay Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Al-Hasan said, \u201cYes, may Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Source: al-Du\u2019a\u0304\u2019 li-T\u0323abara\u0304ni 930 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonlin